OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight rain soon clearing.
OL,6,FThen mostly dry and cloudy during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Rain will spread northeast
OL,8,Facross all parts for a time during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,12,Fnorth, then dry with a few clear
OL,13,Fspells in the evening. Cloud spreads
OL,14,Feast overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FCloudy but dry to start with
OL,17,Fincreasingly bright spells developing
OL,18,Fthrough the morning. Rain likely for a
OL,19,Ftime in the afternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
