OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fwarm with variable cloud and bright
OL,7,Fspells through the weekend and on
OL,8,FMonday. Mainly dry on Saturday and
OL,9,FMonday, but rain for a time on Sunday.
